## Social Platform

| File          | Purpose                               |
| ------------- | ------------------------------------- |
| `settings.py` | Configurations (DB, apps, secret key) |
| `urls.py`     | Main URL routing                      |
| `wsgi.py`     | Needed for deployment (Gunicorn)      |
| `asgi.py`     | Async support                         |
| `__init__.py` | Python package marker                 |
